Title: Babylon 5: The Lost Tales
Writer: J. Michael Straczynski (creator), J. Michael Straczynski
Actors: Bruce Boxleitner, Tracy Scoggins, Peter Woodward, Alan Scarfe
Plot: It's the tenth anniversary of the Interstellar Alliance, and President Sheridan is on his way to Babylon 5 for the celebration. However, he must first deal with a threat from the future, while Lochley handles a case of demonic possession.
